是喙最大的鸟，因此占据了勇地雀和大嘴地雀之间的生态位。 雌鸟的喙是红色的，羽毛是白色、棕色的，带有黑色。雄鸟的喙颜色比较深，羽毛是黑色的。大仙人掌地雀长而有力的喙特别适于吃种子和昆虫。大仙人掌地雀的食物包括种子、水果、仙人掌的花和偶尔也吃昆虫。它们在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛、Genovesa岛和达尔文岛上有分布，往往栖息在仙人掌上。 参考文献", "shortSummary": "大仙人掌地雀（学名：Geospiza conirostris）是一种属于达尔文雀的鸣禽。 伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上的大仙人掌地雀的喙比Genovesa岛上的大仙人掌地雀大。在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上它是喙最大的鸟，因此占据了勇地雀和大嘴地雀之间的生态位。", "habitats": ["灌丛"], "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Geospiza_conirostris_-Espanola_Island%2C_Galapagos%2C_Ecuador-8.jpg/960px-Geospiza_conirostris_-Espanola_Island%2C_Galapagos%2C_Ecuador-8.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "species": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris"}, "expandable": true, "x": -62.52, "y": 29.1, "z": -368.52}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "name": "Geospiza", "latinName": "Geospiza", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Geospiza（Geospiza）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联7种鸟类，如小地雀、大嘴地雀、嗜血地雀等7种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 7, "x": 391.67, "y": -381.52, "z": 81.71}], "links": [{"key": "bird-大仙人掌地雀-9cafc5c3__lives_in__hab-shrubland", "source": "bird-大仙人掌地雀-9cafc5c3", "target": "hab-shrubland", "relation": "lives_in", "label": "栖息于", "evidence": "Its natural habitat is dry shrubland and it is commonly seen on the ground"}, {"key": "bird-大仙人掌地雀-9cafc5c3__has_status__status-vu", "source": "bird-大仙人掌地雀-9cafc5c3", "target": "status-vu", "relation": "has_status", "label": "保护等级", "evidence": "status = VU"}, {"key": "taxonomy-class-aves__belongs_to_phylum__taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "source": "taxonomy-class-aves", "target": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "relation": "belongs_to_phylum", "label": "属于门", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：鸟纲 属于门 脊索动物门。"}, {"key":